        </figure>
      

    
  


  


<h3>Tracking outreach methods</h3><p class="sqsrte-large">The client did not have a setup for website analytics beforehand, so our team connected the site to Google Analytics. Here is an overview of the site analytics from Feb 8, 2021 to March 9, 2021:</p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
