<p class="sqsrte-large">In this section we will point you in the right direction for <strong><em>practicing personal self-care</em></strong>, introducing some <strong><em>WFH (work from home) tips + resources</em></strong>, as well as some <strong><em>remote work communication/project management tools</em></strong> you can use with your team.</p><h1>Practicing Self-Care </h1><p class="sqsrte-large">First thing here is - if your mind is racing and you’re scrolling anxiously - take a deep breath and slow down. You are doing okay because you are doing your best, because you are looking for help and you’ve found it.&nbsp;</p><p class="sqsrte-large">As oversaid as this may be, this is a reminder that everyone is struggling in some area of their life right now because something has been thrown off balance. So, if you are feeling lost or overwhelmed it isn’t something <em>you</em> are doing wrong. That said, let’s try to make it better.&nbsp;</p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5fd6d3753c1f627580a14436/1615439583500-1HDOU0R4COOWM83Z9G8T/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kG87Sfbgg29A4BYEDq3OXvgUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKcf4OxbJOyh_wHUnyc4kQLQ6SBshRGOku7c30Y_IRDNPta8R2IY5BHMaEj1zOWoDTZ/shutterstock_1032198058.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1000x667" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="shutterstock_1032198058.jpg" data-load="false" data-image-id="6049a6dc07206408dc97f4ce" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5fd6d3753c1f627580a14436/1615439583500-1HDOU0R4COOWM83Z9G8T/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kG87Sfbgg29A4BYEDq3OXvgUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKcf4OxbJOyh_wHUnyc4kQLQ6SBshRGOku7c30Y_IRDNPta8R2IY5BHMaEj1zOWoDTZ/shutterstock_1032198058.jpg?format=1000w" />
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  


<p class="sqsrte-large">In order to run a healthy business, you’ve got to make sure it’s being powered by healthy minds and that starts with You. Whether you are a part of management or an employee, getting your own mind to a healthy place will allow you to share that healthy headspace and communicate better with your coworkers.&nbsp;</p><p class="sqsrte-large">You’re busy so let’s cut the fluff. In order to function well you need to:</p><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="sqsrte-large">Eat nutritiously&nbsp;</p></li><li><p class="sqsrte-large">Exercise daily&nbsp;</p></li><li><p class="sqsrte-large">Relax your mind</p></li><li><p class="sqsrte-large">Nourish your mind</p></li></ul><p class="sqsrte-large">Every day, try to commit to at least one thing that ticks those four boxes.&nbsp;</p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
