<p class="sqsrte-large">This is just the beginning for Launch Local and our team is looking forward to helping many more small businesses push through this difficult time. If you or someone you know runs a small business and might benefit from free business and design services, please fill out the form on our <a href="https://www.launchlocal.org/consultation">business services page</a>, or reach out to us via email at <a href="mailto:hello@launchlocal.org">hello@launchlocal.org</a>. We are constantly looking for more people to help and you could help us to help our next client by simply sharing this article or our website with your circle. </p><p class="sqsrte-large">Help us to help those who need it the most; we may be small but we are effective and we are growing.&nbsp;</p>




  
  
    
